   &UR; THE BEAUTY OF BATS &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; TWO COLOR SLIDES ARE AVAILABLE FREE &QL; 
 &UR; (1,000 words) &QL; 
 &UR; By CARL ZIMMER &LR;  &QC;
