Mitchell Zuckoff. 1450 words. GRAPHIC: 38 picas x 4 inches,
``Olympic hopefuls.'' (a and s coding)
</P>
<P>
   w/
</P>
<P>
   OLY-SCANDAL (Salt Lake city) _ The 300-page report by the panel
detailing ethics lapses by the SLOC offers a window into what went
wrong. By John Powers. (2 takes; a and s coding)
</P>
