   &UR; NATIONAL GENERAL &LR;  (``a'' code)
</P>
<P>
   TX-DRAGGING-DEATH (Jasper, Texas) _ Opening arguments get under
way in the trial of the first of three white men accused of killing
a black man by dragging him to death behind a pickup truck. By Rick
Lyman. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &QL;
</P>
<P>
   DARTMOUTH-FRATS (Hanover, N.H.) _ The campus of Dartmouth
College is in an uproar over school administrators' plan to
eliminate the traditional fraternity and sorority system. The move
has underscored a vast social gulf that divides the Ivy League
campus. By Carey Goldberg.  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   NY-IMMIGRANT-DEATH (Conakry, Guinea) _ A two-hour rally outside
the morgue and a government-sponsored prayer service planned for
Amadou Diallo, the immigrant slain by police in New York, whose
body was returned to his homeland by his family on Monday. By Susan
Sachs.
