<TEXT>
<P>
   Fashion stories from The New York Times News Service for
 &UR; WEDNESDAY &LR; , Feb. 17.
</P>
<P>
   WOMENS-FASHION (New York) _ Review of women's fashion
collections by: Steven Di Geronimo, Mary McFadden, Tse, Betsey
Johnson, BCBG, Marc Jacobs, Douglas Hannant, Oscar de la Renta,
Vivienne Westwood and Hugo Boss. By Anne-Marie Schiro. By
Anne-Marie Schiro.
</P>
<P>
   For information and repeats call the News Service at (888)
346-9867 or (212) 556-1927. And be sure to look for other fashion
stories from our partners: Bloomberg News, The Boston Globe, Cox
