   behind schedule, and those that have been delivered rusted
through in only
</P>
<P>
   three years. A new government audit of the troubled $1.2 billion
truck
</P>
<P>
   program says the contractor selected had little experience in
building
</P>
<P>
   combat vehicles. (Malone, Cox News Service)
</P>
