Vancouver Grizzlies, 7:30 p.m.. 
By Randy Hill/Long Beach Press-Telegram. (Will move on the ``s''
sports file.) 
 
 
BKN-LAKNOTE (Inglewood, Calif.) _ Los Angeles Lakers notebook. 
By Howard Beck. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
