QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-NY-MRSCLINTON-NYT, which moved
in ``a'' news file.) 
c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``She hasn't decided to run. I haven't decided to run. I learned
in politics a long time ago that until there is a race everything
is speculation.''
</P>
<P>
   _MAYOR RUDOLPH GIULIANI, about the possible U.S. Senate
candidacy of Hillary Rodham Clinton.
</P>
