<P>
   (NYT1) UNDATED -- Feb. 16, 1999 -- CALIF-VINEGAR-TASTE, 02-16 --
In tasting 28 balsamic vinegars, Molly O'Neill discovered you can't
judge a vinegar by its price tag or its label. These are just a few
of the vinegars that she tasted and rated. (Michael Rogol/New York
Times Photo) *LITE
</P>
